snippet: No. 9 Minnesota used an 18-2 run over the final seven minutes to beat No. 18 Michigan State, 76-63, on Monday.
abstract: College Basketball Men's Roundup; Minnesota defeats Michigan State, 76-63, in its Big Ten opener; other men's and women's college basketball results noted.
lead_paragraph: No. 9 Minnesota used an 18-2 run over the final seven minutes to beat No. 18 Michigan State, 76-63, on Monday.
